<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Thresholds · Richard's Credit Authority</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="nav">
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="brand-logo"></div>
      <div class="brand-text">
        <span>Richard's Credit Authority</span>
        <span>Threshold engine · tax-first</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="index.html">Dashboard</a>
      <a href="loan-application.html">Loan application</a>
      <a href="thresholds.html">Thresholds</a>
      <a href="governance.html">Governance</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <section class="grid-2-balanced">
    <section class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h2>Personal credit thresholds</h2>
        <span class="card-tag card-tag--accent">Authority</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="meta-list">
        <li>
          <span class="meta-label">Total capacity</span>
          <span class="meta-value">$25,000</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="meta-label">Soft warning</span>
          <span class="meta-value">80% utilization</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="meta-label">Hard cap</span>
          <span class="meta-value">100% utilization</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="threshold-bar">
        <div class="threshold-fill" style="width: 50%;"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="helper-text">
        In automation, this page would be driven by a config file or on-chain/off-chain state.
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h2>GitDigital Products allocation</h2>
        <span class="card-tag">Org lane</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="meta-list">
        <li>
          <span class="meta-label">Max GitDigital allocation</span>
          <span class="meta-value">$15,000</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="meta-label">Current GitDigital usage</span>
          <span class="meta-value">$10,000 (66%)</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="meta-label">Remaining GitDigital capacity</span>
          <span class="meta-value">$5,000</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="threshold-bar">
        <div class="threshold-fill" style="width: 66%;"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="helper-text">
        This is the lane your GitDigital Products loans will draw from.
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  Threshold view for <strong>richards-credit-authority</strong>. Static only. Wire to ledger/config when ready.
</footer>
</body>
</html>
